member.name: M:API.ValueObjects.OrganizationName.MyRegex
member.remarks:
Pattern:
^[a-zA-Z0-9\\s&.,'\\-]+$
Explanation:
○ Match if at the beginning of the string.
○ Match a character in the set [&',-.0-9A-Za-z\s] greedily at least once.
○ Match if at the end of the string or if before an ending newline.
